 The Rural Electrification Administration (REA) proposes to amend its interim rule regarding the State Telecommunications
Modernization Plan requirements. The proposed changes are in response to comments received from the public regarding
the interim rule. All Telephone Borrowers will be affected by this proposed rule. 



