Obtaining REA approval of a proposed Modernization Plan. 

 

(a) To obtain REA approval of a proposed Modernization Plan, the Plan Developer must submit the following to REA: 

 (1) A certified copy of the statute or PUC order, if the State is the Plan Developer, or a written request for REA approval
